<h3 class="page-p">Pronoun <em>какой</em> </h3>

<p><span class="eg">Какой</span> is generally used to ask questions about a quality of person or thing and can be translated  as "what kind of" or "which". 

<div class="egdiv">
<h4>Examples: </h4>

<p><em>Какое платье ты ищешь?</em> - Which dress are you looking for?</p>
<p><em>Какую музыку Вы любите?</em> - What kind of music do you like?</p>

</div>
